    <item>
      <title>随着官员考虑市场救援计划，中国股市反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/chinese-stocks-rebound-as-market-rescue-package-mulled</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股市反弹，据称政策制定者正在考虑采取一揽子措施来稳定低迷的市场，这让投资者希望遭受重创的资产类别至少可以在短期内得到缓解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/chinese-stocks-rebound-as-market-rescue-package-mulled</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 02:07:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Codelco 获得股东批准获得首个锂资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/codelco-wins-shareholder-approval-to-secure-first-lithium-asset</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大的铜生产商 Codelco 获得批准收购 Lithium Power International Ltd.，此前这家澳大利亚初级矿业公司的股东投票支持收购，使这家智利矿商的关键能源过渡金属投资组合更加多元化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/codelco-wins-shareholder-approval-to-secure-first-lithium-asset</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 01:59:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国考虑推出2780亿美元的股市救助计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/china-mulls-stock-market-rescue-package-backed-by-278-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，中国当局正在考虑采取一揽子措施来稳定暴跌的股市，此前为恢复投资者信心所做的努力未能成功，并促使李强总理呼吁采取“强有力”的措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/china-mulls-stock-market-rescue-package-backed-by-278-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 01:57:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>秘鲁国家石油公司表示秘鲁政府终究会支持该公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/petroperu-says-peru-government-will-support-company-after-all</link>
      <description><![CDATA[秘鲁政府在一份声明中表示，陷入困境的国有石油公司秘鲁国家石油公司(Petroleos del Peru SA)在一份声明中表示，在总理排除救助计划后，该公司实际上将为其提供财政支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/petroperu-says-peru-government-will-support-company-after-all</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 01:45:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
